column5: One guy was right(ZIB). It was th fuel pump(Diaphram) Had to be rebuilt. Plus they changed the hose. I forgot to get the ends changed too but oh well...  Nice and quick work at Discount RV marina on Keele!  Hopefully I have no problems the next time I am out!!!!!!
That's great Johnny!!!  It took me 6 weeks to get my carbs rebuilt back in the spring!
Let GCD give it a whirl first.LOL Great news John. Go get,em.
right on johnny!!!  Glad to hear you get her fixed up!  Cheers!
I knew it had to be something minor! You look under that hood and it looks like it was just bought!!!  Thanks guys. Hopefully now I can fish without any problems!!!
